{"tid":1741221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"好鄰舍北區教會: 【圍繞理大行區禱告】 ---聲援被困年青人","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:28:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be10314b30191bd8acd65dd4c273760e9a522bad","tid":1741221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"【圍繞理大行區禱告】<br />\n---聲援被困年青人<br />\n<br />\n昔日約書亞圍繞耶利哥行禱，就讓我們學效先賢，以行禱求主施憐憫、拯救！<br />\n<br />\n11月20日(三) 晚上9時30至11時<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會主辦<br />\n主領：陳凱興傳道<br />\n<br />\n祈禱站(遲到者可按時參加)：<br />\n9：30pm 百週年紀念花園(噴水池)(請準時)<br />\n9：45pm 康達徑花園<br />\n10：15pm紅磡車站公共交匯處(巴士總站)<br />\n10：45pm溫思勞街(街尾近天橋位)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如行程有變將即時刊登於教會fb<br />\n<br />\n*此活動以四個祈禱站為主軸，可視為四個小型祈禱會。由一點往另一點時以個別行禱及默禱形式進行(當然有機會同時一起行過去)。以亮起手機燈作燭光以表參與祈禱。<br />\n<br />\n**活動為祈禱會(宗教集會)可獲豁免申請不反通知，歡迎信與未信參加<br />\n<br />\n***請不要灰心，禱告要恆切，不要放棄裡面的年青人！"},{"pid":"b80f3b1666526514aa0864db0eba2f3e5989144b","tid":1741221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7131b32b3a4e783f02839db62c6712160aff3d20","tid":1741221,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a0b392754cb9c55bf608a12dae8f40312d7c77d","tid":1741221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj